    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. The engine has a persistent leak and a heavy knock, and the transmission slips significantly when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It will require a tow and substantial repairs to be safely drivable.",
