    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, well-loved vehicle that's ready to hit the road today! I\u2019ve taken great care of it and kept up with the basics, so it's all set for its next adventure. I'd love to see it go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
