      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of engineering, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a Double VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a functional M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been vetted for subframe integrity, and the cooling system has undergone a preventative overhaul to ensure thermal efficiency under load. With communicative steering rack feedback and a taut suspension setup, this car delivers the precise lateral dynamics and longitudinal poise expected of a well-maintained M-chassis. A true driver\u2019s example where performance-critical components take center stage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
